  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "chapterTitle": "论现代小说",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300043211_8_4789-5064",
          "range": "4789-5064",
          "rangeStart": 4789,
          "rangeEnd": 5064,
          "markText": "生活并不是一副副匀称地装配好的眼镜￼；生活是一圈明亮的光环，生活是与我们的意识相始终的、包围着我们的一个半透明的封套。把这种变化多端、不可名状、难以界说的内在精神——不论它可能显得多么反常和复杂——用文字表达出来，并且尽可能少羼入一些外部的杂质，这难道不是小说家的任务吗？我们并非仅仅在吁求勇气和真诚；我们是在提醒大家：真正恰当的小说题材，和习惯赋予我们的那种信念，是有所不同的。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1718759713,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-19 09:15:13",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300043211&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4789&rangeEnd=5064",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/530326a0813ab7761g01194f?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4789&rangeEnd=5064"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300043211_5_709-781",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "709-781",
      "markText": "“……我很高兴与普通读者们意见一致；因为，在所有那些微妙的高论和鸿博的教条之后，诗坛的荣誉桂冠，最终还得取决于未经文学偏见污染的读者们的常识。”",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300043211&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=709&rangeEnd=781",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/530326a0813ab7761g01194f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=709&rangeEnd=781"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300043211_7_10497-10553",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "10497-10553",
      "markText": "那位女性之中最完美的艺术家，那位写出了不朽杰作的作家，“在她刚刚开始对她自己的成功感到自信的时候”，与世长辞了。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300043211&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10497&rangeEnd=10553",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/530326a0813ab7761g01194f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10497&rangeEnd=10553"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300043211_4_1455-1535",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1455-1535",
      "markText": "一九四一年，《幕间》初稿完成，她对自己探索实验的成果感到不满，德国法西斯的飞机又炸毁了她在伦敦的住宅和出版社，她精神上深受刺激，遂于苏塞克斯的罗得米尔投河自尽。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300043211&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1455&rangeEnd=1535",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/530326a0813ab7761g01194f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1455&rangeEnd=1535"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300043211_4_1280-1379",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1280-1379",
      "markText": "弗吉尼亚·伍尔夫的处女作《远航》于一九一五年问世，从此开始了她的创作生涯。她的作品有《夜与日》、《雅各之室》、《达洛卫夫人》、《普通读者》、《到灯塔去》、《奥兰多》、《海浪》、《岁月》、《幕间》等。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300043211&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1280&rangeEnd=1379",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/530326a0813ab7761g01194f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1280&rangeEnd=1379"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300043211_7_3743-3781",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3743-3781",
      "markText": "一位伟大作家的二流作品是值得一读的，因为它们为他的杰作提供了最好的批评资料。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300043211&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3743&rangeEnd=3781",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/530326a0813ab7761g01194f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3743&rangeEnd=3781"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300043211_4_1714-1790",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1714-1790",
      "markText": "法国著名作家莫洛亚说：“时间是唯一的批评家，它有着无可争辩的权威：它可以使当时看来是坚实牢靠的荣誉化为泡影；也可以使人们曾经觉得是脆弱的声望巩固下来。”",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300043211&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1714&rangeEnd=1790",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/530326a0813ab7761g01194f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1714&rangeEnd=1790"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300043211_25_28755-28828",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "28755-28828",
      "markText": "我们的文学批评以马克思主义的辩证唯物论和历史唯物论为指导原则；伍尔夫的印象式批评拒绝任何理论规范，以批评家本身的常识、直觉、感触、印象为唯一依据。",
      "totalCount": 169,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300043211&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=28755&rangeEnd=28828",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/530326a0813ab7761g01194f?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=28755&rangeEnd=28828"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300043211_25_30231-30280",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "30231-30280",
      "markText": "但是，我们崭新的思想内容，决不是西方社会中那种危机感，而是我们奋发图强建设四化的自豪感和战斗精神。",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300043211&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=30231&rangeEnd=30280",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/530326a0813ab7761g01194f?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=30231&rangeEnd=30280"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300043211_11_8398-8423",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "8398-8423",
      "markText": "生活支配着托尔斯泰，正如灵魂支配着陀思妥耶夫斯基。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300043211&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=8398&rangeEnd=8423",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/530326a0813ab7761g01194f?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=8398&rangeEnd=8423"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300043211_5_1218-1311",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1218-1311",
      "markText": "他的缺陷是显而易见的，因为他只是匆忙地、粗略地、表面地浏览，一会儿抓住这首诗歌，一会儿抓住那部古籍残篇，只要它能为他的目的服务，并且使他的结构成形，他就不管是何处找到的，也不管其性质如何",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300043211&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1218&rangeEnd=1311",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/530326a0813ab7761g01194f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1218&rangeEnd=1311"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300043211_22_5603-5654",
